---

{% from "components/latvija-personas-kods-input/macro.njk" import latvijaPersonasKodsInput %}
{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/field/macro.njk" import field %}

<h2>Default</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "latvija-personas-kods-input-demo", text: "Personal Code" }) }}
  {{ latvijaPersonasKodsInput({ id: "latvija-personas-kods-input-demo" }) }}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>11 digits in the form DDMMYY-CZZZZ where the first 6 are the date of birth (DDMMYY) and C encodes the century (0 = 19th, 1 = 20th, 2 = 21st).</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_identification_number#Latvia">Personal Code</a>.</p>
